															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164265" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;" >sirpudding</a></span> <span class="odate time_1522653255 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">02 Apr 2018 07:14</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3756661">
									

<p>Part III of <em>What the Dead Know</em>.</p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;">psul</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(571081); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(571081); return false;">qntm</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span> for feedback.</p>
<p>Mobile Task Force Tau-5 (&quot;Samsara&quot;) was created by Team Apotheosis: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span> and myself, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=348648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="sirpudding" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=348648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;">sirpudding</a></span>.</p>
<p>Mentioned here are saints MacLaughlin and Vasilev from <a href="/scp-2759">SCP-2759</a> and saints Barnes from <a href="/scp-2959">SCP-2959</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3042342); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3042342&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="TheBillith" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3042342)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thebillith" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3042342); return false;">TheBillith</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1522654741" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2320004); return false;">Rimple</a></span>, respectively.</p>
<p>Readers may find the Identity Warfare Training Primer in the <a href="/sirpudding-s-author-page#toc7">Foundation Universe</a> section of my author page helpful.</p>

